column5: First of all, I did NOT paint or make these. RippinLips did these. I bought the walleye deep divers from RippinLips, and Muskie Metal put the other one together after receiving the painted blades from RippinLips. I'm just showing them as I thought they are a really nice job done on these lures. Can't wait to get them wet. Chuck 🍁🍁
